data.description: Move right in! Beautifully maintained home in tight-knit community offering an open floor plan & vaulted ceilings. Both bedrooms include ensuites. Primary bedroom offers double closets & new glass slider for backyard access. Big ticket items have already been addressed-- 6 yr old water heater, 5 yr old roof, 1 yr old HVAC, 1 yr old carpet, brand new seamless gutters with gutter guards. Avg utility bill for '23 is $100.44. "As is", but beautifully kept. Seller is master gardner.. and it shows!
